# iHerb A/B test experiment cookie value (base64 JSON blob).
# NOT a session token — this is a static feature flag.
#
# How to obtain:
#   1. Open any iHerb product page in Chrome (incognito, cache enabled)
#   2. F12 → Application → Cookies → iherb.com
#   3. Find the "ih-experiment" cookie and copy its value
#
# Paste the value below (without the "ih-experiment=" prefix):
IH_EXPERIMENT=
